The name "Google" is a play on the word "[[googol]]," which refers to the number represented by 1 followed by one hundred zeros.
"Googling" is using the popular search engine Google.com to look up someone's name in an effort to find out more about them. You might Google your neighbor, your old college roommate, or someone you've recently met to see what information is available about them on the Internet.
